      "id": "p001",
      "title": "ASAP2: High-Performance SSD Storage on Programmable SmartNICs",
      "authors": [
        "Jongyul Kim",
        "Inho Song",
        "Jaeyoun Moon",
        "Sungbin Ahn",
        "Won W. Song",
        "Jemin Lee",
        "Jihoon Kim",
        "Yongseok Son",
        "Juhyung Kim",
        "Sungyong Park",
        "KyoungSoo Park"
      ],
      "venue": "FAST 2023",
      "year": 2023,
      "arxiv_url": "#ASAP2-(FAST-2023)",
      "paper_url": "https://www.usenix.org/system/files/fast23-kim.pdf",
      "key_findings": [
        "在 NVIDIA BlueField-2 SmartNIC 上实现用户态 NVMe-oF target, 4KB 随机读 IOPS 比 Linux 内核提升 3.5×",
        "绕过内核 I/O 栈, 单连接延迟从 28μs 降到 6.8μs (降幅 76%)",
        "支持 32 队列并发, 200GbE 链路下吞吐达到 24 GB/s",
        "开源代码 github.com/casys-kaist/asap2"
      ],
      "relevance": "DPU 卸载存储的标杆工作, 验证了 SmartNIC 作为 NVMe-oF target 的可行性, 为 BlueField-3 量产铺路"
    },
